1) code portions to change listening port. (for a chain split that is intended to stay a chainsplit)
2) code portions to signal readiness for the fork. (the versionid thing i was talking about, not sure if versionid is the right word for that) (for a chain split that is intended to be an upgrade)
3) code portions to block noncompliant updates. (for an upgrade chainsplit)
4) replay protection code. (we will need to understand this at some point)
5) PoW change
